      "description": "Get ready to own a masterpiece! This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it was first delivered. It has been meticulously cared for, with a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that still feels brand new. If you're looking for a car that is truly in showroom state, this is the one for you!",
