      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable ride for someone new. It runs smoothly and is ready for many more road trips! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
