    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The vehicle has undergone a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a structural subframe reinforcement, addressing common E46 weak points. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the tactile feedback and neutral handling balance these cars are known for. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver's car, the powertrain remains stout and responsive. An excellent opportunity for the enthusiast seeking an analog, high-performance machine with documented mechanical upkeep.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
