    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly well-maintained example that balances performance with everyday reliability. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips one would expect from careful highway driving. All body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. The upholstery is firm and free of tears, while the dashboard and trim pieces show no signs of sun fading or cracking. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, operates perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has received regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The engine idle is whisper-quiet, and the transmission shifts through all gears with precision. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been treated with respect by its previous owner. I have the complete service history available for your review to ensure total peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
